<br>
1)  Is it an Instant Trigger?  Turn item in and she spawns instantly?<br>
<br>
2)  Does she contain other loot besides the item needed for the epic? <br>
<br>
3)  Does she despawn? If so what's the despawn time? <br>
<br>
Thanks, <br>
<br>
Ally. <p><BR>
<a href="http://www.ichuu.com/cotrd/allyprofile.html" target="AllyProfile"><img src="http://www.ichuu.com/ally58.gif" border="0"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usogaardwildweed.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sogaard Wildweed</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 10:32:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Triggered Faydedar...</span><hr size=1> Ally:<br>
<br>
1) Yes<br>
<br>
2) No<br>
<br>
3) Not sure, but I'd assume he despawns eventually. <br>
<br>
~Sog<br>
~Hierophant<br>
~Lords of Edelo - Innoruuk <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhanahthedruid.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hanah the Druid</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 10:41:54 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Triggered Faydedar...</span><hr size=1> Supposedly, after 2 hours, Fayd goes swimming to the chessboard and gets eaten for dinner by a high lvl npc.  Not sure though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usogaardwildweed.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sogaard Wildweed</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 10:57:55 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Triggered Faydedar...</span><hr size=1> That is what happens to the natural spawn Fay, the triggered one stays in the Oasis as far as I know. :)<br>
<br>
~Sog<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uendorndarkpaw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Endorn Darkpaw</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 11:05:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Triggered Faydedar...</span><hr size=1> my guild as attempted him twice now and twice we have failed... nasty mofo IMHO... But he seemed to despawn after 10 minutes or so if he was triggered. As for the NON triggered version (yes he does exist) he is the 2hour guy... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucuchulainekynthelig.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cuchulaine Kynthelig</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 1:33:41 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Triggered Faydedar...</span><hr size=1> hmm, I would assume he despawns if not killed, but you never know. Probably a good idea to check track as you are headed that way, or you may be in for a nasty surpise as you emerge from the tunnel :p <p><a href="mailto:Cuchulaine@luclin.com">Cuchulaine Kynthelig</a> <BR>
